Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:38.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs28\shad0\fad(0,850)}\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N震动的山(前篇)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.72,0:01:38.32,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是386编队 航路ALL GREEN
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:39.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,准备降至作战高度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.92,0:01:41.86,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,别轻易就被击落喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.96,0:01:43.13,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.45,0:02:03.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,确认矿坑 位置是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.76,0:02:08.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,传送位置坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:18.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,太愚蠢了 简直毫无防备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:30.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,闪身乱打这种招数
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:32.97,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对于没有从太空殖民地降落而来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:35.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,受着重力束缚的联邦的人来说 怎会懂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:37.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,转驻车道 返回矿坑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:40.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,快要遭受舰炮射击了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:43.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:46.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,艾历多亚先生 位置坐标送到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:49.48,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 米凯尔 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:52.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,转送至GUNTANK部队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:55.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,吓死人的数量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:02:58.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然把山都炸得变形了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:00.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,开始啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.67,0:03:01.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.90,0:03:04.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,采用平时一惯的步骤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:06.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,每发射10炮就转移
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:08.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,知道啦 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.57,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,直接命中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:29.26,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好枪法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:32.71,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭这样的战力能守住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:35.99,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心 APSARAS就要完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:37.46,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,而且...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:40.91,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,乘搭凯鲁格连号逃离的准备工作也正在进行当中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.91,0:03:43.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是爱娜小姐特意提出的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:46.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可以回SIDE 3啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:51.49,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 放弃基地 是身为军人无能的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:54.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,矿坑爆破准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:03:59.26,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,摧毁了矿坑的遮门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:02.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,小岛大队07小队进入矿洞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:05.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,能显示影像吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:05.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.21,0:04:07.47,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,连上有线监视器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:09.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没有敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:12.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,快要淹死在米诺夫斯基粒子中了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.74,0:04:14.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,废话少说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:15.66,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是~ 是~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:19.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,发现爆破装置 正在拆除
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.93,0:04:21.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是第4次突入了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:23.31,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这回就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:27.46,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拆除装置前 先让GM撤出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:30.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经失去9台了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:32.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,受重创的是6台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:34.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不是数目的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:35.79,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:40.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,本来对你很期待的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:44.32,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,既然找不到通道进入了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:46.77,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不如把整座山夷为平地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:48.02,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:50.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,除非使用核弹 否则无法轻易就...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:56.48,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,MS的融炉有可能被诱爆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:58.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,光学感应器装备过滤罩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:04:59.61,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,小心被烧坏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,全机 提防冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:07.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,解除警报
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:09.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没发生诱爆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:13.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,只要MS继续使用核能推动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:16.29,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,战场上总会发生意外之事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:19.13,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,难 难道是你故意引爆的!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:23.23,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,「星一号作战」在即
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.77,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要是让那些家伙溜回宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:28.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,被雷比尔发现了 一定会嘲笑我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:30.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.22,0:05:44.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,只能怪你自己跑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:53.57,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,漏掉了1台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:54.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:55.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是“带裙机” 行动非常快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:57.33,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:02.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,上面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:18.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎样攻击都会击中融炉的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:23.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 GM头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:25.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:29.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不过别再叫什么GM头GM头的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:33.41,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,推进剂注入已达70%
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:35.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,倒数计时继续进行中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:38.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呀 在准备起航
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:42.61,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没有收到矿山都市镇压部队的定时联络
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.81,0:06:46.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,凯鲁格连号逃离航路的清扫任务失败了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:48.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,由我来出击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:50.13,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,将弹药补给好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.53,0:06:51.86,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:54.02,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这是仅剩的最后一次补给了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:55.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:59.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想实现爱娜小姐的愿望...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:03.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,空闲的人请到凯鲁格连号上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:05.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,伤员到船上的重力块区去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:08.97,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没有座位的人穿上标准服到货物区去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:15.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,MS 请帮我运送一下伤员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:18.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要留守基地的我们来做这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:20.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是基尼亚斯先生的命令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:22.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,与哥哥无关
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:24.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是我自己要求的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:28.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你让步吧 快去帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:32.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,诺里斯 你平安无事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:37.09,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你总算是说服了基尼亚斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:41.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能让士兵们随哥哥的固执一起殉葬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:43.91,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你变得坚强了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:46.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,因为爱情的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,很意外吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.75,0:07:52.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我并非生来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:56.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,直到走上职业军人之路才这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.55,0:08:02.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜对义父诺里斯你还是一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:06.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我是爱娜小姐的义父？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:08.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不胜荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:11.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我下定决心了 出击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:12.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:15.43,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,现在出击的话就无法与我们会合了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:17.36,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:20.59,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,人活着就是要找出自己的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:23.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,基尼亚斯大人实现了自己的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:23.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,很伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:26.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,爱娜小姐的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:28.41,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是想让凯鲁格连号逃离的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:32.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,实现这个愿望是身为军人的我的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:38.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,请您看好 我定会将逃离航路清扫干净的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:42.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要活着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:43.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.77,0:09:14.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没有办法阻止他了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:21.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,如果... 如果诺里斯有什么不测
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:23.48,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你好运！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:28.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我害死了他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:33.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,到那时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:35.71,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让他自己孤单一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:44.79,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,爱娜小姐把我比作她的父亲呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:56.02,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,山达斯机 完成配置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:58.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲机 配置完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.92,0:10:01.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,全机 准备舰炮射击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:04.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在接到主力部队的指示之前先待机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:05.32,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:06.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.76,0:10:07.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,想吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,安静点！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:11.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是艾历多亚先生当班嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:13.77,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是我曾听到过的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:20.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长先生 吃饭要延迟一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:21.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,有东西正过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:22.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,从哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:25.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 杂音太大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:32.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,升降机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:33.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,从地下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:35.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,山达斯 左前方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:39.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:51.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,指挥车1辆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:52.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,人型机3台
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.97,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,坦克型机3台
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:56.49,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,1台在正下方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.49,0:10:58.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,才1台而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:10:59.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,太小看人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:01.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可他处在我的死角
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:03.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,交给你了 卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,人型机配备了光束武器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:12.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对速度慢的凯鲁格连号是种威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:17.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:20.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,他从通风口进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:22.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:24.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可以预测他的动向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:28.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:33.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:36.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,第1台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:49.59,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我和山达斯都被他玩弄了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:52.73,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,一瞬间就解决掉1台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:55.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这个家伙是... 王牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:08.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,连逃脱的路都帮我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:09.86,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:12.71,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,视界很差
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:14.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,艾历多亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.07,0:12:15.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:16.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你来指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.89,0:12:18.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什么~ 什么~ 什么~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:21.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,从我这边无法知道那家伙的动向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:23.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你的耳朵比较可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:26.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好极 包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:28.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,08小队 听好本大爷的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:30.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.11,0:12:31.04,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么了~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:33.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没有 什么也没说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:34.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,山达斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:35.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:37.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:39.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,改换指挥了 知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:42.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,他的方向感最好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:46.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不像是他能办到的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:54.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,想制造烟幕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:58.62,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,去你那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.62,0:13:00.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:04.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 会从哪里过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:14.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:17.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:20.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:24.29,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要攻击驾驶舱吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:31.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,曹长 让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:43.47,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,逮到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:46.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在649-223号高架桥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:48.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,301射击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:50.97,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩1台
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:59.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,APSARAS的最终检查正在启动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.31,0:14:04.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,ALL GREEN
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:06.32,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,APSARAS完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:11.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好长的一段路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:14.32,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:15.77,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.63,0:14:26.66,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:32.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,请好好地品尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:41.02,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,艾历多亚 帮了我大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:49.66,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:13.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,颤抖吧 惊惧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:16.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没有办法发挥MS性能的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:17.62,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就等着受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:19.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,防守好就不会输了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:20.36,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:37.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:39.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我加倍奉还给你！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:46.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,盲目攻击只会出丑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:49.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,坦克已任由我宰割了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:53.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要赶上！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:12.02,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,爱娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:14.73,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不能与你会合了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:19.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到了自己死亡的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:27.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,爱娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:30.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,诺里斯大佐发出了烟雾信号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:33.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什么颜色的？诺里斯怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:35.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是红色...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:41.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,无法会合 凯鲁格连号起航吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:42.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:45.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,凯鲁格连号起航准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:47.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,驱动动力导管 解除开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:49.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:52.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,分别虽然是件痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:55.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可时间已经到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:58.74,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:08.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,APSARAS是我一个人的东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:14.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,距凯鲁格连号起航还剩不到20分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.52,0:17:16.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候转守为攻了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:25.47,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没子弹了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:46.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是左手被打废了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:56.77,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,反射神经倒不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:59.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这招你躲得掉吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:08.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,漫不经心可是会致命的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:29.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 主回路在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:30.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:35.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:36.71,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么还不来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:47.57,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,一枪杀了我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:51.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢救命之恩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.37,0:18:53.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,少啰嗦 快点走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:56.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 队长代理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:58.29,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,去背箱那里拿武器的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:19:01.29,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 那样做会被干掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:03.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,总之要死守坦克 死守！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:06.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,也该玩够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:10.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.37,0:19:13.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,机师还活着的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:16.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,来了 山达斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:17.57,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:22.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,手... 快按我说的做呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:26.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴... 301呀...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:30.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么要活着回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:34.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么为了同伴而战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:38.61,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我... 在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:48.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我... 要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:54.66,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,呵 醒过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:11.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我！要活着！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:14.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,活下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:16.91,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,与爱娜再次相会！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:18.13,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你家伙是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:20.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:25.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长他！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:27.97,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,恢复啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:32.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,摆脱了困扰的傻瓜还真是厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:34.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,复活了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:37.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这个声音...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:41.62,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是闲聊的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.62,0:20:43.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,爱娜酱要出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.36,0:20:54.77,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:57.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:58.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.77,0:21:05.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:32.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然会遇上爱娜小姐思念的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:35.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是有趣的人生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.78,0:21:37.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:46.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.09,0:21:55.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.37,0:22:09.77,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,输了...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.10,0:22:38.73,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,大家听好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.33,0:22:40.73,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我要离开军队了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.55,0:24:19.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.95,0:24:21.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,山达斯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.80,0:24:24.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,艾历多亚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.85,0:24:26.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,米凯尔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.85,0:24:28.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.40,0:24:31.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,还会再见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.65,0:24:41.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,下回
